pull_request.title: Deprecate OQS-OpenSSL-1.0.2
pull_request.body:
Recent changes to liboqs (https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/tree/6d87c34ddab112c40f189af678021b3a154de680) mean it no longer works with our OpenSSL 1.0.2 fork.  This PR deprecates OQS-OpenSSL-1.0.2 and freezes the version of liboqs it worked with.

- Remove from CircleCI
- Update README
- Fix build to use the last working version of liboqs master (https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/tree/ac03b344679ffec6666376c1d955e1c7e30937e3)
